接口 ResultCallback<R extends Result>

所有已知实现类：

public interface ResultCallback<R extends Result>

An interface for receiving a Result from a PendingResult as an asynchronous callback.

方法摘要
 void onResult(R result)
          Called when result is returned It is the responsibility of each callback to release any resources associated with the result.
 

方法详细信息

onResult

void onResult(R result)
Called when result is returned It is the responsibility of each callback to release any resources associated with the result. Some result types may implement Releasable, in which case release() should be used to free the associated resources.

参数：
result - The result from the API call. May not be null.
